  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Randomized controlled trial to evaluate the efficacy of oral iron supplementation in reducing
      the prevalence of preoperative anemia in a cohort of 82 patients undergoing elective
      prosthetic hip or knee surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
